Pair them with light-colored jeans or go wild with shorts and long socks. The classic high-cut sneakers is a versatile piece to match any of your outfit dreams.

Handcrafted with a full canvas upper, unique cap-toe design and debossed metal aglets, our OCA High exists at the intersection of style and comfort.

Completed with our signature lightweight memory foam technology and a durable vulcanized rubber sole, we bring you a sophisticated and comfortable sneaker unlike any other.

And suddenly, there was PANTONE 18-1750 Viva Magenta—not a murmur, but a shout of euphoria and a new signal of strength, to guide us through the year 2023. PANTONE 18-1750 Viva Magenta is a shade descending from the red family, an animated red tone that welcomes anyone and everyone with the same verve for life and rebellious spirit.

**STANDARD shipping takes about 5-6 business days to arrive.**

Our standard return window is **60 days**! Returns and exchanges are accepted if your sneakers are: **Unworn**, **Unwashed**, and **In the original packaging**

When trying on your CARIUMAs for the first time (to test fit & comfort), please make sure to only wear them inside on a clean floor. If you plan to return them (or think there’s a slight chance you might need to exchange them), we ask that you refrain from wearing them outside. This eliminates the possibility of dirt, grime, etc. We cannot accept any sneakers that have been worn down, disheveled, washed or altered in any way.

